    <string name="app_name">Hunting Log Helper</string>

    <string name="welcome_text">
        "This app was created to assist tracking hunting logs and crafting logs in FFXIV."
        "The logs are organized by class. Hunting logs show the name, the amount needed, the region/area where the monsters are found and the x and y position of the dungeon."
        "There is no exact position of the monsters within the dungeon.\n"
        "Crafting logs are also organized by class and show the required level, ingredients and skill to craft an item.\n"
        "Both monster and item icons are available as an optional icon pack (due to the extra size of 35 MB) which can be downloaded in the settings.\n"
        "The app was designed and written by Michiyo, with the help of Naomi (Data entry, etc) and Forecaster (Data scraping).\n"
        "The hunting and crafting logs were scraped from http://ffxiv.gamerescape.com\n"
        "Make sure to keep the app up-to-date to ensure having the latest updated logs."
    </string>
